MyNXT,is,a,decentralized,way,to,use,a,mobile,wallet,This,is,an,open,source,tool,that,allows,users,to,take,control,of,funds,without,downloads,installation,or,hassle,The,API,service,is,about,interaction,with,the,myNXT,info,online,wallet,and,performance,of,standard,NXT,queries,Every,time,a,developer,makes,a,call,to,the,myNXT,info,API,the,site,will,determine,the,best,server,to,process,the,request,All,servers,work,on,HTTPS,mode,providing,security,through,the,calls,that,should,be,made,through,this,method